    "This method has shown effectiveness, yielding promising results in automating selecting the number of phases and clusters for fitting PH distributions.",
    "Having obtained the parameters from the abovementioned process, we construct the Probability Density Functions (PDFs) with mixture distributions.",
    "Following this, the reliability evaluation methodology is carried out in a series of steps:• The first step involves collecting data associated with the system's behavior over time.",
    "This data should include information about the various states of the system, along with the time required for transitions between these states.",
    "• Using the collected data, we estimate the parameters of a Phase-Type (PH) distribution."
